    <h3>We met at Jimbo's (it was all a dream)</h3>
    <p>
    The story of Meghan and Chris started like most other love stories, at a party at Jimbo's house in Rhode Island. Legend has it that Meghan's sister, Amy, tried to pair Chris and Meghan that night. Unfortunatley that's not how this story ends; however, Jimbo's is only the beginning of Meghan and Chris' story.
    </p>
    <h3>Move over Virginia, New Hampshire is actually for lovers</h3>
    <p>
    It was a snowy, cold, and dark night in the bitter mountains of New Hampshire. Meghan and Chris went skiing together with a large group of friends. The night of this ski trip is where Meghan and Chris, two people destined for each other, finally fell in love. They spent the night talking about everything, and through this conversation, they realized they couldn't possibly be without each other in life anymore. A few short weeks later it was official, Meghan and Chris were DATING.
    </p>

