    <h3>Oh, the places you'll go</h3>
    <p>
    The relationship between yours truly was filled with many experiences. From getting hit by a car, to moving states away, to moving back to Boston. Meghan and Chris have been everywhere together, enjoying everything life offers -- and experiencing it the way it was meant -- with each other.
    </p>
    <p>
    Meghan is from Connecticut and Chris is from Massachusetts. Thankfully, Meghan's family is a smart group of people, and were fans of all boston's teams. The first few years of there relationship was semi-long distance. Meghan was at school in boston, and Chris worked in Cambridge. This allowed them to see each other at least a few times a week. But the summers were difficult, Meghan returned home to Connecticut, and Chris had to remain in Massachusetts. They saw each other every weekend, never wanting to spend time without the other. They even met halfway sometimes just to have dinner in the middle of the week.
    </p>
    <p>
    The toughest stage of the relationship was after college. Meghan moved back home to work on the set of the renouned "Jerry Springer Show". Chris still remained in Massachusetts after finding another job in the area. Again, they had to see each other on the weekends, and endure the grind of driving through multiple states just to see each other for fleeting moments, before returning to their weekly lives.
    </p>

